Want to make reading content online easier…and faster?
Brave’s Speedreader feature can help with both, by automatically removing nonessential elements from the webpage. It’s a clean and efficient way to read, get what you need, and get on with your day.
Want to try speedreader? Just open an article in Brave, and click the speedreader icon Brave speedreader icon that appears beside the URL in the address bar.
